<p>You're in luck, Dodger. We've tracked down Petter Vangen's head secretary. And good news, she lives nearby! Go check her out, I've attached her address and contact information. If you get nothing from her, just in case, I'm attaching info on some other people who may have information on Mr. Vangen's current whereabouts.</p>
<p>Don't give up, Dodger, you've made more progress by yourself than everyone else on this mission combined! Good luck!</p>
<p>Caecilia Cortez<br />
Signature stuff<br />
MCF</p>
